                    "body": "If you want to build with {{MinSizeRel}}, you'll need to add \r\nhttps://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-15664#\r\n{code}\r\nelseif(\"${CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE}\" STREQUAL \"MINSIZEREL\")\r\n  set(CMAKE_C_FLAGS \"${CMAKE_C_FLAGS} ${C_FLAGS_MINSIZEREL}\")\r\n  set(CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS \"${CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS} ${CXX_FLAGS_MINSIZEREL}\")\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nto https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/fa699117091917f0992225aff4e8d4c08910162a/cpp/cmake_modules/SetupCxxFlags.cmake#L633-L647 for that to work",
                    "updateAuthor": {
